110
00:07:03,467 --> 00:07:07,533
Is it okay to shoot like this, all messy?

111
00:07:07,533 --> 00:07:09,133
Mr. Song, I'm sorry.

112
00:07:09,133 --> 00:07:10,933
I'll do better next time.

113
00:07:10,933 --> 00:07:12,900
Yeo Reum, please stick to the script.

114
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:16,733
No, why are you doing this to me?

115
00:07:16,733 --> 00:07:20,633
We need to get residents' quotes...
But, not even a single ant passes by.

116
00:07:20,633 --> 00:07:23,533
What's with these random vendors and dog noises?

117
00:07:23,533 --> 00:07:27,767
What am I even doing here right now?

118
00:07:27,767 --> 00:07:31,733
<i>I want to ask too. What are you doing?</i>

119
00:07:33,367 --> 00:07:35,533
<i>As usual today...</i>

120
00:07:35,533 --> 00:07:38,900
Alright, let's try again.

121
00:07:39,533 --> 00:07:43,400
<i>But I'm a pro,</i>

122
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,733
<i>so today I'll smile</i>

123
