232
00:12:57,733 --> 00:13:00,000
Take that back.

233
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,433
Words have power too.

234
00:13:02,433 --> 00:13:05,367
Anyway, don't say things
like that, even as a joke.

235
00:13:05,367 --> 00:13:07,300
Ah, look at the ledger.

236
00:13:07,300 --> 00:13:09,100
How is this a company ledger?

237
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:11,467
It's just a bankrupt household budget.

238
00:13:12,933 --> 00:13:16,533
But, we still have

239
00:13:16,533 --> 00:13:18,700
two precious artists.

240
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:19,800
Yes, yes.

241
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:22,033
[Yoo Ha Na]
The three artists we had are now down to two,

242
00:13:22,033 --> 00:13:25,300
and one is serving in the military
after being called by the country.

243
00:13:25,300 --> 00:13:27,700
I'm most scared about his discharge.

244
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:29,333
What are we doing with these operating expenses?

245
00:13:29,333 --> 00:13:31,800
We'll have to move out
of this office next month too.

246
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:33,767
Ms. Yoo,

247
00:13:35,533 --> 00:13:39,400
in life, there are always ups and downs.

248
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:41,533
We're a company that once produced

249
00:13:41,533 --> 00:13:43,800
both a girl group and a boy group.

250
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:46,600
Those stars Go Eun Chae, Cha Si Wan...

251
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,633
are gone now.

252
00:13:47,633 --> 00:13:51,800
But, they all came from our company once.

253
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:54,367
Finance Director, what's wrong with you?

254
00:13:55,533 --> 00:13:57,767
This so-called Finance Director,

255
00:13:57,767 --> 00:14:00,300
no money, no connections,

256
00:14:00,300 --> 00:14:03,600
no staff, how can that be a Finance Director?

257
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:04,933
Just give that title to...

258
00:14:04,933 --> 00:14:06,867
